snippet.title: Roma and Diana plays at the 3D Art in Paradise MUSEUM, Fun for kids activities
snippet.description:
Roma and Diana fun plays at the MUSEUM in Bangkok. Art in Paradise - is great fun for kids and families to spend a few hilarious hours. The new 3D Art in Paradise in the Bangkok is a shiny and spotless 2 storey gallery packed with superbly executed paintings in which visitors are invited to be part of dozens of scenes. The children had fun playing this MUSEUM - 3D Art in Paradise 
Instagram Diana: https://www.instagram.com/kidsdianashow/
